#Full list of tests to perform
#To remove a test simply comment it out
#Tests ending with '*' will not be compared with the control tests
#They are generally just useful system output and will be sent in
#Full with every set of errors.

system* # A few commands to identify details of the platform
test # A simple echo to make sure the suite is working

#fail # A test guaranteed (chance 100!:1) to fail
#BCCD # Test some built-in BCCD commands
#GalaxSee # Test the GalaxSee program
#Life # Test John Conway's Game of Life
